Mo ta bai toan:
Gia su co 1 cong viec la in ra man hinh n lan ki tu x.
1.in ra man hinh ki tu x.
2.in ra man hinh so tu nhien tu 1-n.

lam the nao de giai quyet viec:
displayChar("x") 500 lan 10s
displayChar("b") 1000 lan 20s
 displayNumber(100000) 20s
 
 10 + 20 + 20 => lan luot
 
 => su dung da luong: 20s (max)
 
 Giai phap:
 1. Tao ra cac nhiem vu.
 2. viet lop ke thua tu Thread (class built-in cua Java)
 3. add viec nao Thread de goi thuc hien.
 